Name: Missile Input
About the game: UFO sightings have grown exponentially the last few months, and the Secret Service is spread too thin to devise convincing cover-ups for all of them. The solution? Enlist the help of Lucas Brazier; a former brass worker turned surface-to-air missile specialist. As the newest recruit in the fleet of AA-privateers, your job is to shoot down any and all UFOs spotted in the sky. Will You Follow Orders? Typing gameplay with multiple difficulties Special missiles and equipment to buy Two factions to help or destroy Unlockable extras, including Boss Rush, Survival and Target Library Aliens Missile Input features the musical work of Nicolas.
